snippet.title: Reunion: A Jeff The Killer Game | Full Game + All Jeff Kill Animations
snippet.description:
Reunion is a short 3D Horror Game made for the #luigikidex3challenge

It's been 3 years since the loss of your Parents. Now you've got out of the Orphanage and you want to find your missing Brother, which might still be alive somewhere.

Download Link: 
https://gamejolt.com/games/reunion-jtk/808735
or
https://tayo-o.itch.io/reunion-jtk

This game is an unofficial continuation of the "Jeff The Killer" Creepypasta.
